sp_500_daily_returns_tbl <- sp_500_prices_tbl %>% 
  select(symbol, date, adjusted) %>% 
  filter(year(date) >= 2018) %>% 
  group_by(symbol) %>% 
  mutate(prev_adjusted = lag(adjusted)) %>%

  mutate(pct_return = diff / prev_adjusted) %>%
